9 Relating to public transportation in counties having a
10 population of 600,000 or more; to amend Section 11-32-7, Code
11 of Alabama 1975, to provide that a transit authority is
12 authorized to participate in business organizations relating
13 to transit operations, land acquisitions, and activities
14 incidental to the operation of the authority; to create,
15 establish, acquire, operate, or support subsidiaries of the
16 authority; to make or arrange for loans for the activities of
17 the business organizations; to provide that the business
18 organizations with which the authority participates shall not
19 have the power of eminent domain; to revise Section 11-32-2,
20 Code of Alabama 1975, to make conforming changes; and to make
21 nonsubstantive, technical revisions to update the existing
22 code language to current style.
23 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
